CommandDoccommentNode.comment:
`iterate n tac` runs `tac` exactly `n` times. `iterate tac` runs `tac` repeatedly until failure.
`iterate`'s argument is a tactic sequence, so multiple tactics can be run using `iterate n (tac₁; tac₂; ⋯)` or ```lean iterate n tac₁ tac₂ ⋯ ``` -/
